      <title>美国大型科技股狂热推动发达市场股市创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/us-big-tech-mania-drives-developed-market-stocks-to-record-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，约 61 万亿美元的发达市场股票全球基准升至历史新高，华尔街科技巨头领涨。]]></description>
